<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>Notification_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`Notification`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>simple<sp/>wrapper<sp/>around<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>notification<sp/>object<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>Its<sp/>primary<sp/>purpose<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>facilitate<sp/>communication<sp/>and<sp/>logging,<sp/>offering<sp/>a<sp/>Python-friendly<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>C++<sp/>notification<sp/>functionalities.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>lightweight<sp/>and<sp/>efficient,<sp/>enabling<sp/>seamless<sp/>integration<sp/>of<sp/>C++-level<sp/>notifications<sp/>into<sp/>Python-based<sp/>workflows.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>Notification_class<sp/>The<sp/>Notification<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
