<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>is<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty,<sp/>as<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>object<sp/>is<sp/>initialized<sp/>in<sp/>`__init__`.</highlight></codeline>
